   sustainable development including sustainable development impacts at
   1.5°C and 2°C, the synergies and tradeoffs of mitigation and adaptation
   with the Sustainable Development Goals/SDGs, and the possibilities for
   sustainable and equitable low carbon, climate-resilient development
   pathways,

   Executive Summary
     * View
     * Download
