   First Order Draft submitted to TSU 20 April 2018
   TSU compile First Order Draft 23-30 April 2018
   Expert Review of First Order Draft 4 May-29 June 2018
   TSU send compiled review comments to CLAs 6 July 2018
   Third Lead Author Meeting 23-28 July 2018
   Cut-off date for submitted papers 15 October 2018
   Second Order Draft submitted to TSU 19 October 2018
   TSU compile Second Order Draft 22 October-12 November 2018
   Expert and Government Review of Second Order Draft 16 November-11
   January 2019 2018-19
   TSU send compiled review comments to CLAs 18 January 2019
   Fourth Lead Author Meeting 4-9 March 2019
   Cut-off date for accepted papers 15 May 2019
   Final Draft submitted to TSU 31 May 2019
   TSU compile Final Draft 3-10 June 2019
   Final government review 14 June-9 August 2019
   51st Session of the IPCC: Approval of the Summary for
   Policymakers, accepting the underlying Report 20-23 September 2019

